These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | milk | sprite | tea   |
| Sport      | tennis    | ice-hockey  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, juice, mirinda
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, italian
1. the american is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the colombian is on the far left##1
3. the colombian is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | juice | water     | mirinda      |
| Nationality   | colombian | american | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, sprite
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cherry, kale
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | milk | sprite  | coffee       |
| Food       | asparagus     | cherry | kale |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, peach, nectarine
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, fishing, drawing
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | nectarine    | peach     | apricot |
| Hobby   | drawing | video-games | fishing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, hamster
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, ship, snowmobile
1. the person driving the ship is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | dog | ferret     | hamster |
| Transport   | snowmobile        | boat | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, cranberry, potato
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard, bike
1. the person eating lime is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person eating potato is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | potato | lime      | cranberry  |
| Transport   | helicopter       | skateboard | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, electronic, ambient
3 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, snake
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of electronic is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | indie     | electronic    |
| Pet           | rat | snake | turtle |

 #################################

 
