3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, pony
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | fishing | dancing | sudoku  |
| Pet     | pony     | hedgehog      | bird |

