.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, family, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | fanta   | hot-chocolate    | lemonade    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | spy | disaster |

