There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, chinese, egyptian
1. the fan of country is the mexican##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the egyptian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | house | country   | soul  |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | mexican | chinese |

