The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, manager, coach
1. the manager is on the right of the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating pear is in the middle##1
3. the designer is on the right of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
