.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, d&b, jazz
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | milk | cola  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | jazz   | house |

