2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | skydiving | reading |
| Music-Genre   | techno | r&b     | ambient  |

