.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, grapefruit, kale
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, ice-hockey, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | kale | lemon       | grapefruit  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | ice-hockey | parkour |

 